text: Makhachkala (; Lak: Гьанжи; Avar: МахӀачхъала; Lezgian: Магьачкъала; Rutul: МахаӀчкала) is the capital city of the Republic of Dagestan, southwestern Russia. As of the 2010 census, the city had 572,076 people living there. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Capitals of republics of Russia Category:Cities and towns in Dagestan
title: Makhachkala
